metrics_conclusion: Heavy Light has higher complexity than the average song  in terms Chord Complexity and Chord Progression Novelty.
key_conclusion: Heavy Light has sections analyzed in the following keys: E Minor, E Phrygian,  and A Minor.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: With this one, I tried using multiple voices and instruments to get the tabs as close as possible to the real song. It took approximately forever and I'll probably never do it again, but I think it turned out OK. Uploading to Theorytab turns them into standard piano, so I'll link to the full versions in the comments: http://www.hooktheory.com/hookpad/view/iSLGTbIRgZcy
